These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, horror
3 different pets are kept: pony, turtle, horse
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the person watching epic movies and the owner of the turtle##7
2. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | martial-arts | epic |
| Pet           | turtle  | horse     | pony  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, gospel, pop
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, boat, train
1. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the fan of pop and the person driving the boat##7
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | pop |
| Transport     | boat       | train     | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, airplane, helicopter
1. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person driving the trike##7
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | soy-milk | fanta | milk  |
| Transport   | helicopter  | airplane  | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, librarian, freelancer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, animation, romance
1. the writer is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the librarian##7
2. the person watching animation movies is not the writer##6
3. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | librarian | writer | freelancer     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | sports          | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, blues, classical
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, bike, airplane
1. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the fan of blues##7
2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b      | classical     | blues   |
| Transport     | airplane | bike | scooter |

