.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, techno, disco
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, turkish, russian
1. the spanish is on the left or right of the turkish##3
2. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
3. the fan of techno is on the right of the russian##1
4. the fan of techno is somewhere between the russian and the fan of classical##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | techno     | classical     |
| Nationality   | russian | turkish | spanish |

