.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: horse, lizard, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, ice-hockey, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person who's sport is skiing##7
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | rabbit       | lizard      | horse       |
| Sport   | skiing | volleyball | ice-hockey |

