.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, woodworking, camping
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, pilot, librarian
1. the librarian is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
2. the pilot is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the designer is somewhere between the pilot and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | camping | baking   |
| Job     | librarian    | designer  | pilot |

