.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, fanta
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, weightlifting, snowboarding
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | tea   | fanta    | lemonade |
| Sport      | snowboarding | lacrosse | weightlifting |

