2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the japanese is not the person who's hobby is puzzles##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | puzzles | hiking | card-games |
| Nationality   | russian    | indian    | japanese         |

