.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, tomato, raspberry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, thriller, horror
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching drama movies is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person eating blueberry##7
3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | blueberry  | raspberry       | tomato     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | drama | thriller |

