.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-14::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, plum, mango
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, quad-bike
1. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
2. the person driving the quad-bike is the person eating plum##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person eating apple##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food        | plum | mango | apple |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | snowmobile       | taxi      |

