The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, golf, rugby
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is golf##7
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Pet     | frog  | guinea-pig       | chinchilla    |
| Sport   | badminton | rugby | golf |

