.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-16::.
There 3 different types of food: orange, cherry, kale
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, argentine, brazilian
1. the person eating orange is somewhere to the right of the person eating kale##5
2. the person eating kale is the person eating kale##1
3. the person eating cherry is somewhere between the brazilian and the australian##7
4. the australian is the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | kale | cherry     | orange   |
| Nationality   | brazilian   | argentine | australian |

