.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, coffee
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, teacher, nurse
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the accountant##1
2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the teacher##7
3. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the teacher##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | juice      | coffee     | fanta |
| Job        | nurse | accountant | teacher    |

 